{"tid":2456100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登賭盤] 美國即將新增一州，到底傳說中既第51州係邊？","createTime":"2021-03-21T15:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T15:42:22.000Z","uid":52658,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"2187138df0b3e4261db89cd734d0d655fea28a5c","tid":2456100,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"拜登選前話過 佢上台後會考慮新增一州<br />\n今日3月21 拜登上左台都兩個月<br />\n但佢本人都好似無再重提呢件事<br />\n<br />\n佢今期係做4年既<br />\n如果係連登開賭盤 <br />\n邊個地方可以最先成為美國第51州？<br />\n條件：每人只準買一次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n波多黎各州<br />\n1:0.7<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞州<br />\n1:1.1<br />\n<br />\n下加州<br />\n1:2<br />\n<br />\n東田納西州<br />\n1:4.9<br />\n<br />\n太平洋州（夏威夷州以外所有美國殖民地）<br />\n1.6.1<br />\n<br />\n紐約市州<br />\n1:6.8<br />\n<br />\n南德州<br />\n1:8.9<br />\n<br />\n西阿拉斯加州<br />\n1:9.7<br />\n<br />\n楓葉州：<br />\n1:269<br />\n<br />\n台灣州<br />\n1:408<br />\n<br />\n中國州<br />\n1:950<br />\n<br />\n賴比瑞亞州<br />\n1:1000<br />\n<br />\n截至2024年1月12日 美國並無新增州份<br />\n1:0.8"},{"pid":"7676bf2b3308036e825f63d0a678b24b0250f2cb","tid":2456100,"uid":1354,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"香港"},{"pid":"f9d7511d6b3e9b9451187a5de62b7ea708be69ad","tid":2456100,"uid":256286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"51?"},{"pid":"194b0b1ee44598c9bc42f58cf14b953d65614628","tid":2456100,"uid":24284,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"華盛頓dc?"},{"pid":"d1174e9914d96d6d3271fce9f1595d99dab194c6","tid":2456100,"uid":52658,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"7676bf2b3308036e825f63d0a678b24b0250f2cb","tid":2456100,"uid":1354,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"香港"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"香港一賠2億都得<br />\n美國州份係要比美國統治過先有資格建州<br />\n中國有上海 天津美租界<br />\n台灣都可以拗以前曾係聯合國託管地<br />\n你香港建州 完全係違憲"},{"pid":"9c3b06ef03b47eae9b6750c0e